com.github.seqware.queryengine.model
Class Tag

java.lang.Object
  com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.impl.AtomImpl<Tag>
      com.github.seqware.queryengine.model.Tag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Atom<Tag>, Buildable, Taggable, Versionable<Tag>, Serializable
public class Tag
extends AtomImpl<Tag>

A Tag an instance of a TagSpec which contains all three of the values necessary for a GVF (ex: ID=ID_1 or Variant_seq=A,G or Reference_seq=G ). Tags always have subjects, they have a default predicate "=" and they may or may not have objects. A non-specified value is represented as null Tags themselves are immutable (and thus do not need Versionable but adding and removing tags on objects is of course possible given the right permissions
